            <fr:addr type="user">FA-0016</fr:addr>
            <fr:route>FA-0016.xml</fr:route>
            <fr:title text="Conjugate">Conjugate</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
            <fr:date>
              <fr:year>2025</fr:year>
              <fr:month>5</fr:month>
              <fr:day>26</fr:day>
            </fr:date>
            <fr:authors>
              <fr:author>Long Nguyen</fr:author>
            </fr:authors>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <fr:p>The complex conjugate of a complex number <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[z = a + bi]]></fr:tex>, denoted as <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\bar {z}]]></fr:tex> or <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[z^*]]></fr:tex>, is defined as:</fr:p>
            <fr:p>
              <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\bar {z} = a - bi]]></fr:tex>
            </fr:p>
            <fr:p>where <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[a]]></fr:tex> is the real part and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[b]]></fr:tex> is the imaginary part of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[z]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
            <fr:p>Key properties of complex conjugates include:</fr:p>
            <fr:ul><fr:li><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\overline {z_1 + z_2} = \bar {z}_1 + \bar {z}_2]]></fr:tex></fr:li>
<fr:li><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\overline {z_1 \cdot  z_2} = \bar {z}_1 \cdot  \bar {z}_2]]></fr:tex></fr:li>
<fr:li><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\overline {\bar {z}} = z]]></fr:tex></fr:li>
<fr:li><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[|z|^2 = z \cdot  \bar {z} = a^2 + b^2]]></fr:tex></fr:li></fr:ul>
            <fr:p>In the context of <fr:link type="local" href="FA-0013.xml" addr="FA-0013" title="Inner product">inner products</fr:link> on complex vector spaces, the conjugate symmetry property states that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\langle  u, v \rangle  = \overline {\langle  v, u \rangle }]]></fr:tex> for all vectors <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[u]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[v]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
          <fr:backmatter />
        </fr:tree>
